"一意専心の力試し・Ⅱ":
"Hey, doing good work out there?
I think rather than challenge each
area one by one in time attacks,
it'd be better to handle multiple areas
at once. That's why I've decided to start
requesting people finish their favorite
time attacks 3 times and reward them
for it. Why not give it a go?
※Completa cualquier time attack 3 veces
en Muy Difícil o +."
